<div class="container">
  <% if @answer == 'yes' %>
  <p>I'm a musician!</p>
  <form action="/submit" method="post">
    <input type="hidden" name="authenticity_token" value="<%= form_authenticity_token %>">
    <p>1. To allow conveniences such as finding musicians near you, you may need to enter your personal address. Will you be willing to store your personal address?</p>
        <input type="radio" name="address_first" id="add_yes" value="yes">
        <label for="add_yes">Yes</label>
        <input type="radio" name="address_first" id="add_no" value="no">
        <label for="add_no">No</label>

    <p>If not, will you be willing to just enter your zipcode/city?</p>
      <input type="radio" name="address_response" value="Yes">
      <input type="radio" name="address_response" value="No">

    <p>2. Since Note Jam emphasizes on meeting each other in real life, are you comfortable with signing up with your real name instead of an alias? (Only your first name will be displayed)</p>

    <p>3. Will you be willing to meet complete strangers to form a band?</p>

    <p>4. If you had spare space, will you be willing to rent it out for other people to use?</p>

    <p>4b. To you, what sounds like a reasonable price of renting a place for a 2 hour session? </p>

    <p>5. Are you comfortable with using Paypal for peer to peer payments? </p>

    <p>6. Based on the description of our services, how likely will you use the site? (1 for least likely, 10 for most)</p>


    <input type="submit" name="" value="">
  </form>
  <% else %>
  <p>I'm not a musician!</p>
  <!-- buy/sell -->
  <p>1. Would you use Notejam in order to market any products or services related to music?</p>
    <input type="radio" name="market" id="add_yes" value="yes">
    <label for="add_yes">Yes</label>
    <input type="radio" name="market" id="add_no" value="no">
    <label for="add_no">No</label>
  <p>2. If your products/services were sold would you be comfortable using paypal?</p>
    <input type="radio" name="payment" id="payment_yes" value="yes">
    <label for="payment_yes">Yes</label>
    <input type="radio" name="payment" id="payment_no" value="no">
    <label for="payment_no">No</label>
  <p>2b. Would you rather meet up locally to sell a product or prefer online payments?</p>
    <input type="radio" name="location" id="Local" value="Local">
    <label for="Local">Local</label>
    <input type="radio" name="location" id="Online" value="Online">
    <label for="Online">Online</label>
    <input type="radio" name="location" id="Both" value="Both">
    <label for="Both">Both</label>
  <p>2c. If you offered lessons would you rather meet with the client, or have the client come to you?</p>
    <input type="radio" name="meet" id="meet" value="meet">
    <label for="meet">Meet with client</label>
    <input type="radio" name="meet" id="come_to" value="come_to">
    <label for="come_to">Client comes to me</label>
<!-- looking for gigs -->
  <p>3. If you wanted to book a gig for an event, with the ability that this website would offer information about the band, would you use this website to contact the band?</p>
    <input type="radio" name="contact" id="contact" value="contact">
    <label for="contact">I would rather contact the band</label>
    <input type="radio" name="contact" id="web_contact" value="web_contact">
    <label for="web_contact">Have the website contact the band</label>
  <p>3b. Would you rather directly contact the band or have them be notified of interest?</p>
    <input type="radio" name="notify" id="notify" value="notify">
    <label for="notify">Notify them directly</label>
    <input type="radio" name="notify" id="web_notify" value="web_notify">
    <label for="web_notify">Have them be notified by the website</label>
  <p>3c. Would you pay based on performance or would it be a flat rate?</p>
    <input type="radio" name="pay" id="hourly" value="hourly">
    <label for="hourly">Hourly rate</label>
    <input type="radio" name="pay" id="flat" value="flat">
    <label for="flat">Flat rate</label>
<!-- rent -->
  <p>4. Would you use our website to rent out an available space for a band?</p>
    <input type="radio" name="rent" id="rent_yes" value="rent_yes">
    <label for="rent_yes">Yes</label>
    <input type="radio" name="rent" id="rent_no" value="rent_no">
    <label for="rent_no">No</label>
  <p>4b. If yes, would you rather accept a flat rate or hourly?</p>
    <input type="radio" name="rent_pay" id="rent_hourly" value="rent_hourly">
    <label for="rent_hourly">Hourly rate</label>
    <input type="radio" name="rent_pay" id="rent_flat" value="rent_flat">
    <label for="rent_flat">Flat rate</label>
  <p>4c. If your whole house was available, would you rent the whole property our or just a certain space?</p>
    <input type="radio" name="rent_space" id="rent_room" value="rent_room">
    <label for="rent_room">Just a room</label>
    <input type="radio" name="rent_space" id="rent_whole" value="rent_whole">
    <label for="rent_whole">The whole property</label>
  <p>4d. If a band contacted you to rent, would you rather use AirB&B or NoteJam?</p>
    <input type="radio" name="choice" id="airbnb" value="airbnb">
    <label for="airbnb">AirB&B</label>
    <input type="radio" name="choice" id="notejam" value="notejam">
    <label for="notejam">NoteJam</label>
<!-- rating -->
  <p>5. Based on your experience with a band/client/vendor, would you prefer to rate the person/group?</p>
    <input type="radio" name="rating" id="rating_yes" value="rating_yes">
    <label for="rating_yes">Yes</label>
    <input type="radio" name="rating" id="rating_no" value="rating_no">
    <label for="rating_no">No</label>
  <p>Any other additional comments (optional)</p>
  <div class="row">
      <form class="col s12" action="/submit" method="post">
        <%= tag(:input, :type => "hidden", :name => request_forgery_protection_token.to_s, :value => form_authenticity_token) %>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="input-field col s12">
            <textarea id="textarea1" class="materialize-textarea" data-length="120" name = "optional"></textarea>
            <label for="textarea1">Textarea</label>
            <input type="submit" name="" value="Submit">
          </div>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>
